Aston Villa fans sing 'Glory, Glory' ahead of FA Cup final
Media playback is not supported on this deviceA selection of Aston Villa fans sing their famous song 'Glory, Glory' ahead of their appearance in the FA Cup final on Saturday.Villa will take on cup holders Arsenal in a bid to win the famous trophy for the first time since 1957.Watch the FA Cup final live: Arsenal v Aston Villa on Saturday 30 May at 17:15 on BBC One and the red button.